<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <%- include('partials/styles') %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">ACCOUNT<span>GUARDIAN</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="badge badge-info">WELCOME</div>
    <h1>Welcome to Account Guardian, <%= merchantName %>.</h1>
    <p>Your Stripe account monitoring is set up. Here's what happens now and what you can expect.</p>

    <ul class="checklist">
      <li>We're capturing your account signals — dispute rate, refund rate, chargeback rate, and transaction patterns</li>
      <li>We're establishing your personalized baseline — so alerts are about <em>your</em> normal, not industry averages</li>
      <li>We'll email you the moment any signal crosses its threshold — so you can act before Stripe does</li>
      <li>You have full access to your dashboard with signal history and trend visualization</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Your <span class="highlight">14-day free trial</span> has started. After the trial, monitoring continues at <strong>$79/month</strong> with no surprise charges — cancel any time from your dashboard settings.</p>

    <div class="action-box">
      <h2>First step: Check your dashboard</h2>
      <p>Your dashboard shows your current signal values, baseline thresholds, and alert history. Visit it now to see your account health at a glance.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="cta">Go to Your Dashboard →</a>

    <div class="footer">
      Account Guardian by Astramedia · Monitoring Stripe accounts so you don't get surprised<br>
      Questions? Reply to this email.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
